# Licensing & attribution

This repository is an **unofficial, non-commercial community archive** of
**guidesnotincluded.com**, an *Oxygen Not Included* guides site created by
**"Some Random Finn"** (contact on the original site: `somerandomfinn` at
`proton.me`). The original site is offline; this archive was rebuilt from the
**Internet Archive** (Wayback Machine) and reformatted from HTML to Markdown.

Different parts of this repository are covered by different terms.

## 1. The guide content (everything under `docs/`, excluding images)

The textual guides were published by the original author under a
**Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike** licence. The author's
own statement (preserved on the "Complete Beginner's Guide" page) reads:

> "This guide is published under a CC-BY-NC-SA license. Which basically means
> non-commercial use/reuse of my scribblings is fine."

The original did not pin a version, so this archive applies and redistributes
the text under **CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 International**:

> https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/
> Legal code: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/legalcode

What that means here:

- **BY — Attribution.** Original work © Some Random Finn / guidesnotincluded.com.
  Every page links back to its source URL and Wayback snapshot, and notes that
  it was reformatted. Keep that credit if you reuse the content.
- **NC — NonCommercial.** This archive is not monetised (no ads, no payment).
  Do not use the content commercially.
- **SA — ShareAlike.** This archive (an adaptation/reformatting of the original)
  is distributed under the same CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 licence. Redistribute any
  derivative under the same terms.

**Changes made in this archive:** crawled from the Wayback Machine, main content
extracted from the original Wix HTML, converted to Markdown, images localised,
and site navigation/boilerplate removed. A few pages are incomplete because the
source captures were incomplete or unavailable.

## 2. Images (`docs/assets/`)

Per the original author, the images come from several sources — the
**Oxygen Not Included Wiki**, the author's own **gameplay footage**, and
**images by Klei**. They are **not** all the author's own work and are therefore
**not** covered by the CC BY-NC-SA licence above. They are reproduced here for
non-commercial, archival/reference purposes only:

- *Oxygen Not Included*, its art, screenshots and assets are © **Klei
  Entertainment**. Game imagery is used under Klei's community/fan-content
  allowances; all rights remain with Klei.
- ONI Wiki imagery remains under the wiki's respective terms.

If you are a rights holder and want an image removed, please open an issue.

## 3. Build & guide credits (third parties)

Individual builds and techniques are credited in-page to their original
creators, including **Francis John**, **Jahws**, **Mullematsch**, and the
broader *Oxygen Not Included* community (Reddit, Steam, YouTube). Those credits
are preserved in the restored pages.

## 4. The crawler / tooling (`scripts/`, `mkdocs.yml`, workflows)

The restoration tooling in this repository was written by the repository owner
and is provided as-is for archival use. It is independent of the content
licence above.

